{"tid":2051922,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"多國議員成立聯盟　旨在推動集體對中國採取更強硬政策","createTime":"2020-06-05T06:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T07:44:51.000Z","uid":288699,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1db2d31f38da37b4bb6c9d2e5e40f1936c4db1c2","tid":2051922,"uid":288699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:29:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】來自八個國家和歐盟的十多名國會議員組成「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」，旨在推動各國政府集體對中國採取更強硬政策，關注包括香港等問題。<br />\n<br />\n這十九名國會議員，來自美國、加拿大、英國、德國、挪威、瑞典、澳洲和日本八個國家及歐洲議會。<br />\n<br />\n發起人是英國保守黨前主席施志安，他說全球商界都應該關注對華政策跨國議會聯盟關注的議題。他特別提到滙豐銀行公開支持中國推行港區國安法，指滙豐銀行的舉動「令人震驚」，他說多國議員對加入聯盟反應踴躍，尤其是瑞典和德國，反映中國真正已令不少人擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393399\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393399&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=a81e5760\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D393399&h=ef8932df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=393399</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醒覺左，要一齊揾中共追數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"670c38e929132cd139579e43025c67d8a1e3e96a","tid":2051922,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"風起了"},{"pid":"242c5cfa355d87adaf16cbbf47e3fb3a54dbf8aa","tid":2051922,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34f13597b922cf66e95352db3bcbf95d58760f1","tid":2051922,"uid":75610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"通識可以出條支那促成政治全球化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf117e2a1d792db43c9dbfc47e7cc00c920b5146","tid":2051922,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":